{"tid":2179944,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"8.31一周年，你有樣野可以做","createTime":"2020-08-29T13:13:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T16:57:21.000Z","uid":264429,"like":111,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"5569671e805b497760a418251f967f73238baa3e","tid":2179944,"uid":264429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T13:13:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0aoJQd3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0aoJQd3.jpg&h=1f3728e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">【8.31 重拾罷鐵初衷】</span></span></strong></em><br />\n<br />\n國安法生效至今，不少人都感到無力，不知道前路何去何從。然而，每天日常生活中仍有很多可做之事，罷搭黨鐵便是其一。<br />\n<br />\n你還記得8.31當日的憤怒嗎？魔警於黨鐵將市民打到頭破血流，急救員跪地哭求仍無法入站救人。黨鐵事後更拒絕公開閉路電視片段，罷鐵風潮因而展開。至今，當日死傷數字未明，魔警及黨鐵卻在法網外逃之夭夭。然而，不少同路人亦因各種原因，重新拍卡走進了黨鐵月台。<br />\n<br />\n星期一將是8.31一周年，讓我們重拾初衷，全民罷搭黨鐵，堅守生活中每一寸可抗爭的土壤。<br />\n<br />\n抗爭未竟，唯拒絕遺忘、堅持到底，才能看見出路。"},{"pid":"84170e55d25e17e14e9df159276c6950208a09b1","tid":2179944,"uid":6845,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T13:14:02.000Z","msg":"一定"},{"pid":"53c88e47ce9e276d3aad93d2fa4fe4f4ca3f53ac","tid":2179944,"uid":279463,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T13:15:25.000Z","msg":"this is a must"},{"pid":"c925defe9e1402276887eefd14996878975feb8e","tid":2179944,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T13:17:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcb34cda08bb02cee9171d37bc37064ed68aacea","tid":2179944,"uid":231583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T13:17:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"69013551ab0669dda1be0fb8221bf46e035cf4b2","tid":2179944,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T13:18:07.000Z","msg